OL,3,CUnion welcomes move to reduce train
OL,4,Cdriver training age to 18
OL,6,FMoves to reduce the age at which train
OL,7,Fdrivers can begin training have been
OL,8,Fwelcomed by their trade union.
OL,10,FAslef said legislation to reduce the
OL,11,Fage from 20 to 18 will be brought
OL,12,Fbefore Parliament on Tuesday, which it
OL,13,Fbelieves will lead to drivers better
OL,14,Freflecting their communities.
OL,16,FGeneral secretary Dave Calfe said:
OL,17,F"Aslef has been campaigning for many
OL,18,Fyears to lower the age at which
OL,19,Fdrivers can start training.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
