OL,3,CUnion welcomes move to reduce train
OL,4,Cdriver training age to 18
OL,6,F"This decision, to allow people to
OL,7,Fleave education and become a driver at
OL,8,F18, will increase diversity in the
OL,9,Fdriver's cab by encouraging more young
OL,10,Fpeople from all communities to drive
OL,11,Ftrains on Britain's railways.
OL,13,F"At the moment, many young people make
OL,14,Ftheir career choice at 18 and the
OL,15,Findustry misses out as the current
OL,16,Fminimum age is 20.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
