OL,3,CUnion welcomes move to reduce train
OL,4,Cdriver training age to 18
OL,6,F"This change will widen the
OL,7,Fopportunity for the rail industry to
OL,8,Frecruit the large numbers of train
OL,9,Fdrivers required over the next five
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,F"It offers young people the
OL,13,Fopportunity of secure employment ` to
OL,14,Fget a job in a highly unionised
OL,15,Findustry with good pay, and good terms
OL,16,Fand conditions, in contrast to the
OL,17,Fshort-term and insecure jobs in the
OL,18,Fgig economy which are, so often, all
OL,19,Fthat is available to young people
OL,20,Ftoday."
