OL,3,CUnion welcomes move to reduce train
OL,4,Cdriver training age to 18
OL,6,FAslef said reducing the age from 20 to
OL,7,F18 brings it into line with London
OL,8,FTube train drivers and with other
OL,9,FEuropean countries such as Germany,
OL,10,Fthe Netherlands, and Switzerland.
OL,12,FRob Kitley, who chairs Aslef's Young
OL,13,FMembers' Committee, and a driver with
OL,14,FGWR, joined the railway eight years
OL,15,Fago.
OL,17,FHe said: "It's fantastic to see the
OL,18,Flegislation now being put in place for
OL,19,Fthe reduction in the minimum train
OL,20,Fdriver age to 18.
OL,26,@yD@JOU
