OL,3,CUnion welcomes move to reduce train
OL,4,Cdriver training age to 18
OL,6,F"As young train drivers we have been
OL,7,Fcampaigning for this change for many
OL,8,Fyears, in order to level the playing
OL,9,Ffield and bring our industry into line
OL,10,Fwith other parts of public transport,
OL,11,Fsuch as buses and the London
OL,12,FUnderground.
OL,14,F"By widening the goal posts to allow
OL,15,Fyounger candidates to join the driving
OL,16,Fgrade, we open the door to new talent
OL,17,Fwhich may otherwise have been lost.
OL,19,F"This helps to safeguard the role and
OL,20,Four industry for the future."
